description.displayText: Jack is one of the most energetic, responsible, compassionate and capable people I know. He has helped us in the past with my elderly father, my nieces and nephews, our dog and some of the neighbors' dogs and with running errands. He is a real self-starter and doesn't require a lot of direction. He is cheerful and a hard worker who really cares! I would never hesitate to recommend him for any job!
